Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,ABAN, THE HERO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a story of Aban, the Hero...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:02:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}from the days of his youth\Nas a member of the Order of Carl.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time to grasp the world\Nin my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forth, my monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn their towns! Wreck their countries!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wipe out the pathetic humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Against the mighty Dark Lord Hadorra\Nand his monster legion...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the humans could do nothing\Nbut tremble in fear.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But one kingdom stood resolute\Nin the face of the Dark Army's invasion.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Under their new lead knight, Roka...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the elite Order of Carl faced\Nthe Dark Army as an unparalleled force.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Carl Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Princess Flora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, hear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much the Dark Army\Ntramples our world and burns our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,there is nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Lord is the one who fears!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For we humans have the power to unite!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I will join in the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Together with our proud Order of Carl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess is so brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In place of its bedridden king,\NPrincess Flora led Carl Kingdom.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With her beauty and courage,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:04:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flora was a goddess of hope\Nto the world.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well spoken, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm merely doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you who should be praised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of the Order,\NI see he's missing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see Aban is his usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go fetch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare he skip out on\Nthe Princess's public appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Roka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No it's not! I'll go discipline him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Something's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This soup is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! But I made it for you, Sir Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is in the flavoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:05:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you grind a Feverfew stem\Nand mix it in, it should come together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Feverfew is good for illness\Nand injuries, plus it's quite nutritious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For our secret flavor,\Nwe add a pinch of Seeds of Agility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know so much, Sir Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you taste my soup next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Roka. Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop playing innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just in time.\NSome bread with this soup is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Sir Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, what is with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You skipped guard duty\Nfor a cooking class?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But as the strongest in the Order,\Nyou're enough of a bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Improving the food that everyone eats
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is a much better way for me\Nto serve the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my friend, but I have no idea\Nwhy you were chosen for the Order of Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably because I study.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zinuar family comes from\Na long line of scholars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! We're in the age of war now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling when the Dark Lord\Nwill target our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in just studying\Nand being fawned over by girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to practice your sword skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes that's important, but surely\Nyou intend to have a family someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You might have an adorable child\Nwho takes after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't at least know how to cook...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! I'm devoting my life to the sword!\NI don't need a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ever get married,\NI'll run across the entire country naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, at least practice\Nso you can defend yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stance may need work,\Nbut you can at least practice swinging!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Roka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a war is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood writing just appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What language is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Darkling Language.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a communication spell\Nsent through mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The writing says this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tonight, I shall come\Nto claim the Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as a sacrifice to\Nthe God of the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Lord."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Lord wants the Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency! Increase our security!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Roka, castle security\Nis on high alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Dark Lord! Come if you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Roka, where is Aban?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he had important business\Nand went off into the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The woods?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more important\Nthan your safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise we'll protect you\Neven without that coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn you, stupid Aban!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You may not be strong,\Nbut I never thought you'd run away!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As of today, you and I are through!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Dark Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone at the ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You filth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I summon you, my monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Derupa!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thrash the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Monsters are attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Where did they come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! He's so powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come to claim you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold! The Dark Lord himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Lord, I know what you're up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A sacrifice to the God of the Underworld\Nis just a cover story!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,By stealing me away through any means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you intend to demoralize my people\Nand hasten your domination of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Very sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're young, but you're still a ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This will save me a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now kneel before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like I can kill you right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:10:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be submission or death?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Which do you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! Make your choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:28.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEGIRAMA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NHEAT-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:33.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IONAZUN{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NEXTREME-EXPLOSION SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like I can kill you right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be submission or death?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Which do you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! Make your choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Dark Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be more gentle\Nwhen trying to seduce a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me your nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. This Magic Bullet Gun\Nneeds more work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just sprinkled it with\Na little Coagulant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Coagulant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little secret compound I cooked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters sprinkled with it\Nlose their minds and attack each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The monsters outside\Nare fighting each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I sprinkled some on the ones outside, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And now your trusty monster legion\Nhas been rendered useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see! He went to the forest\Nto find Poison Moths!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not bad, you trickster!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You worm! You dare humiliate me\Nwith your conniving trickery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sense from this frail man... Aura?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one\Nwho's going to pay, Dark Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've seen that before!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That expression on Aban's face!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was three years ago.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In my youthful lust for adventure\NI snuck out of the castle alone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban was the one who rescued me when\NI was attacked by a monster in the forest.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I told him who I was\Nand recommended him to the Order.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, once he joined,\Nhe began wearing those dud glasses...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and acted as though\Nhe couldn't fight at all.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was like he was suppressing\Nhis immense power.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I could tell.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He acted that way because\Nhe didn't want to show off.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Princess.\NBut I'm still a member of the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Should the need arise, I shall use all my\Npower to protect you and Carl Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But until that time comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I will keep what I know\Nabout you a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're saying the time has come, Aban?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! You're not\Npicking a fight with me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sit by and watch someone\Nhurt others for their own ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't assume I'm that naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merami!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He can use spells?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a human,\Nhe uses highly advanced magic!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I never knew Aban was that strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over! {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merazoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad show.\NBut you're still just a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:17:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to my magic,\Nyours is a trivial thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can even use Ionazun?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! If I dodge, he'll hit the Princess!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! You'd choose your own death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case... Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Roka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I got him good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't cast that spell now, can he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well! A Iora spell will suffice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll reduce you all to ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare hurt my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IORA!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this blinding light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban defeated the Dark Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No. The Dark Lord still lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was really dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that arm would crumble to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's proof he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Very observant!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I suppose I will retreat for now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you won't defeat me\Nwith that paltry power! Ever!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With my current power\NI can't defeat the Dark Lord.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're leaving, Aban?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your symbol of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the day you defeat the Dark Lord\Nand save the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall hold on to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Amulet of Carl\Nwhich is passed down in the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will help you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kiseiseki that has been made\Nusing a Zinuar family secret process.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one left who can make these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd give me something so valuable?\NAre you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider it a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Roka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming with you, Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to pay the Dark Lord back\Nfor what he did!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! Without the captain of\Nits Order, who will protect Carl Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! We can leave it to\Nthe ones that I've trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we can't do much\Njust defending ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to go on the offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The best defense is a good offense!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no guarantee that we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're facing the Dark Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw hope in\Nthat blade of light of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was by accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Coincidental or still incomplete,\Nit still drove the Dark Lord back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in that light!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After much intense training,\Nthat blinding strike...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was completed to become the Aban Strash.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Aban...{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Strash!{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:12.08,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:18.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:23.88,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:29.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:35.64,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:41.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:47.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:53.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:59.21,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:01.83,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:05.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:10.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:16.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:22.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:25.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:30.07,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To bind with the legendary\NGreat Purification Spell, Minakator,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leona and the others brave\Nthe Cave of Trials where monsters roam.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.92,0:23:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Dai enlists the aid of Nova\Nto train with his sword.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The remaining Popp learns of a mysterious\Npower hidden in the Insignias of Aban.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.22,0:23:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Cave of Trials"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.56,0:23:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
